xt-1">According to the Health and Social Care Information Centre, the UK's population is becoming increasingly diverse. Projections suggest that minority ethnic groups will make up over 30% of the population by 2050.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hAcGzb caRPsV pf-33_ pf-text-1">Research by the Social Care Institute for Excellence (SCIE) indicates that individuals from minority ethnic backgrounds often face disparities in access to social care services and experience poorer outcomes compared to their white counterparts.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hAcGzb caRPsV pf-35_ pf-text-1">The Care Quality Commission (CQC) has identified inequality in care provision as a significant concern, emphasising the need for robust equality and diversity policies and practices in social care settings.</li></ul></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gIDmLj bESFPC pf-37_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Navigating_Legislation_ComplyPlus_for_Children_s_Home_Regulations_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1710431109" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Navigating_Legislation_ComplyPlus_for_Children_s_Home_Regulations_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1710431109 1536w" width="1612" height="1228" alt="Navigating Social Care Equality and Diversity: Best Practices Unveiled - ComplyPlus LMS™ - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Navigating Social Care Equality and Diversity: Best Practices Unveiled - ComplyPlus LMS™ - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-jQrDum jseZXh pf-38_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-eLwHnm fPjVqe pf-39_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by  Rawpixel via Envato Elements</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-jrQzAO jIEVBe pf-41_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column